    {
      "text": "V-71983",
      "system": "http://cyber.mil/legacy"
    },
    {
      "text": "CCI-000366",
      "system": "http://cyber.mil/cci"
    },
    {
      "text": "CCI-000778",
      "system": "http://cyber.mil/cci"
    },
    {
      "text": "CCI-001958",
      "system": "http://cyber.mil/cci"
    }
  ],
  "fixtext": {
    "text": "Configure the operating system to disable the ability to use the USB Storage kernel module.\n\nCreate a file under \"/etc/modprobe.d\" with the following command:\n\n# touch /etc/modprobe.d/usb-storage.conf\n\nAdd the following line to the created file:\n\ninstall usb-storage /bin/true\n\nConfigure the operating system to disable the ability to use USB mass storage devices.\n\n# vi /etc/modprobe.d/blacklist.conf\n\nAdd or update the line:\n\nblacklist usb-storage",
    "lang": "en",
    "fixref": "F-4573r462538_fix"
  },
  "fix": {
