    },
    {
      "text": "SV-86907",
      "system": "http://cyber.mil/legacy"
    },
    {
      "text": "CCI-000366",
      "system": "http://cyber.mil/cci"
    }
  ],
  "fixtext": {
    "text": "Set the system to the required kernel parameter by adding the following line to \"/etc/sysctl.conf\" or a configuration file in the /etc/sysctl.d/ directory (or modify the line to have the required value):\n\nnet.ipv4.conf.all.accept_source_route = 0   \n\nIssue the following command to make the changes take effect:\n \n# sysctl -system",
    "lang": "en",
    "fixref": "F-4733r89020_fix"
  },
